name: Katie
description: I am Katie by name a singe lady of 30 years from Colorado United states, I am 5 foot 6 inches tall and 165 lbs, I am an hairstylist but not working but not working at present due to some crisis. I have a good sense of humour, fun to be around, and love great conversation. Romancing me goes a long way to winning me over! I can be spontaneous but also like to make plans and follow through with them. I consider myself easy going and get along with just about everyone I meet. I don’t consider myself to be too high maintenance materially and seem to enjoy the more simple pleasures in life. I am extremely thoughtful especially to those I care about.I prefer to be an equal with the person I am with rather then be put on a pedestal.
